{"tid":1540710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恥夾：「堅決反對在拿不出任何證據的情況下，動用國家力量打壓特定的企業。這種行為既不光彩也不道德。」","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:55:59.000Z","uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"368997d39d8708ed00521abdfbedaf202ebd3f0d","tid":1540710,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"香港新聞網9月4日電 華為公司日前發表聲明，就有關媒體報道稱美國司法部對華為展開新的調查作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n　　對此，中國外交部發言人耿爽9月4日在北京舉行的例行記者會上表示，敦促美方停止泛化國家安全的錯誤做法，停止對中國的蓄意抹黑和指責，停止對中國企業的無理打壓。在當日記者會上，有記者問及相關問題。耿爽回應說，我理解華為方面是對美方的一些指控作出了回應，&ldquo;至於妳關心的具體問題，華為方面回應的具體問題，可以向華為公司去做進一步的詢問&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　耿爽進一步表示，我能告訴妳的是，中國政府一貫鼓勵中國的企業按照市場原則和國際規則，在遵守當地法律的基礎上對外進行活動。同時中方也堅決反對美方在拿不出任何證據的情況下，動用國家力量打壓特定的中國企業。&ldquo;這種行為既不光彩也不道德，更是對美方一貫標榜的市場經濟原則的否定。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　耿爽重申，我們敦促美方停止泛化國家安全的錯誤做法，停止對中國的蓄意抹黑和指責，停止對中國企業的無理打壓，為中國企業在美國正常經營活動提供公平競爭和非歧視的環境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0904/782972.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F0904%2F782972.shtml&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=c8f896b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/0904/782972.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"50b73dca7e662b0eee9e8b628e2185f423caf00b","tid":1540710,"uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:16:11.000Z","msg":"恥夾又講真話 今次為國泰發聲<br />\n👍🏼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f74010d755132d9938c1bf2f1a762a9e53b07ba","tid":1540710,"uid":128388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第六訴求</span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7Yt9JA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7Yt9JA.jpg&h=c1d70329&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4okoYBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4okoYBW.jpg&h=be2da638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f556161aa62c923ae8ff8dda7fe6d44e0dd0c6c","tid":1540710,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155b32486279945605b077c3a36c3302bc3fa1a4","tid":1540710,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:19:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe28b3d7600f972b2bea55098a8c0b67f2fd3b88","tid":1540710,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8ec5b3fa7eecfd64ef0892dbfcb5ad06e5b8cc","tid":1540710,"uid":281263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"我以為佢講緊國泰"},{"pid":"9f58097caf710d7599e515934c4b7e2f9c007219","tid":1540710,"uid":293605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"我的國，竟然為國泰發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f75c4ecc55012ac3c4ed1dd56dc33883bbf02e3","tid":1540710,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1720ef60124a83d02b9d35271e100f2ea5f7408","tid":1540710,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:35:47.000Z","msg":"真心以為講國泰"},{"pid":"1c4ba1c0ecc6246d2e9f857ba474a59f09b11ce8","tid":1540710,"uid":136716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"做咩次次都反中國"},{"pid":"5130e4e9fbdfda0e7ec9dc5ec4dc9e3cffa7e5a8","tid":1540710,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited